```{.r .cell-code}
library(gt)
library(gtExtras)
```
:::


## load data

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
eurovision <-
  readr::read_csv(
    "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/rfordatascience/tidytuesday/master/data/2022/2022-05-17/eurovision.csv"
  )
```

::: {.cell-output-stderr}
```
